CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

December 27, 2006

[Cite as 12/27/2006 Case Announcements, 2006-0hio-6712.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2006-1681. Moody v. Coshocton Cty.

Wayne App. No. 05CA0059, 2006-Ohio-3751. On review of order certifying a conflict. The court determines that no conflict exists. This cause is therefore dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell and Lanzinger, JJ., concur. Resnick and Pfeifer, JJ., dissent.
